headline: International Paper CEO describes wins, challenges with transformation plan
summary: CEO Andy Silvernail dug into the company’s ongoing optimization and how recent changes in Georgia play a role in long-term return on investments, during a Sept. 4 session at the Jefferies Industrials Conference.
